title: Why Bernie Sanders loves Denmark but Hillary Clinton doesn’t
text: Raise your hand if you had " Hillary Clinton defends capitalism, and/or criticizes Denmark " in your office pool for the first on-stage debate fight of the Democratic primaries. That's right - you didn't. But Clinton's extolling of the free-market economic system, and her critique of Democratic socialism, was her first open attack on the man closest […] ...
